ISLAMABAD, Apr 09 (APP): Minister for Information and Broadcasting Chaudhry Fawad Hussain on Saturday said that rumours that a change in the leadership of the Pakistan army was being considered as very absurd and baseless.
In a tweet, he said that such rumours were being spread under a plan and the government condemned and completely denied these rumours.
